column13: name changed to ADBRI in may 2020

Event Hospitality & Entertainment Limited on 17 December 2015. own brands Event Cinemas, Moonlight Cinema, Cinestar, Greater Union, GU Filmhouse and Birch Carroll & Coyle brands. Also includes the ownership of the Sydney-based State Theatre, and Edge Digital Technology, a cinema technology supplies company. Encompasses the ownership and management of hotels in Australia, New Zealand and the United Kingdom through the Rydges, QT Hotels + Resorts, Eventhouse and Atura Hotel brands. Also includes the ownership of Thredbo Alpine Village, located in New South Wales
